snippet.title: 'Aquaman': Amber Heard On The 'Strong, Motivated' Mera & Working With Jason Momoa | Access
snippet.description:
At Cinemacon 2018 in Las Vegas, Amber Heard shares with Access her passion for playing Mera in "Aquaman." Plus, what was the costume process like? And, Amber tells Access about working with Aquaman himself -- Jason Momoa.
